name: Senility #4 (Albert Einstein)
description: This is the fourth work in senility series. Getting older is a gift of life too, the gift titled "The Second Childhood". Yes, one may exhibit undesired changes like a loss of cognitive abilities, such as memory. But hey, that's perfectly fine as we knew nothing when we came to this world. This artwork is dedicated to the greatest physicists of all time, who defeated senility.
